import React from 'react' const CoinBlock = (props) => { //debugger return (
{props.name}
Price: {Math.floor(props.price)}$
Price change: {((+props.price_change_prc).toFixed(2))*100}%
{props.market_cap.length >= 13 ? '$'+(+(props.market_cap/1000000000000).toFixed(2))+'T' : true} {props.market_cap.length < 13 ? '$'+(+(props.market_cap/1000000000).toFixed(2))+'B' : true}
{props.name}
) } export default CoinBlock
